  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761684/", 
  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761684\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tAs hardly as a film in science are <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/entirely\" target=\"_blank\">entirely</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/separate\" target=\"_blank\">separate</a> cultures, we're currently seeing a whole series of titles in which science features from creating biology in Under the Skin to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cosmology\" target=\"_blank\">cosmology</a> in Interstellar, to early computer science in The Imitation Game. And we'll soon have The Theory of Everything about the marriage of physicist Stephen Hawking. Followed by Ex Machina, a drama about <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/artificial\" target=\"_blank\">artificial</a> intelligence, all these films have that <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/essential\" target=\"_blank\">essential</a> factor, the scientific adviser, and that can be you, Adam.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;And indeed, it has been. I think that science fiction cinema is gonna surely reach <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/saturation\" target=\"_blank\">saturation</a> point in 2015, we're gonna have a new Star Wars, a new Jurassic Park, a reboot of Mad Max, the final Hunger Games. The Terminator will be back again, and The Avengers will be avenging once more. Now, not all of them did, but there has been a trend of late for Hollywood to turn, not just to science for inspiration, but to actual real bona fide scientists to do, well, what.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\tWe're coming to the end of the British Film Institute's national Sci-Fi season, Days of Fear and Wonder, which featured everything from <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/blockbuster\" target=\"_blank\">blockbuster</a> galaxies far, far away to obscure and often weird space oddities.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761684/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p761684\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761731/\">歪果仁也追太子妃升职记：五毛钱国剧你赢了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761789/\">最易记住的10个英文单词 不用背就知道！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761788/\">语言点精析：卡梅伦2016新年贺词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761771/\">囧研究：女人最爱自黑的五个点 你中枪了么</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761709/\">考据党观影报告：10个神探夏洛克大电影彩蛋</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761634/\">搞笑野生动物摄影奖：一个个都是影帝啊！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761738/\">2015负能量新闻TOP5：满屏逗比都忘吃药了吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p760669/\">心灵鸡汤：学学自信的人都是怎么做的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761575/\">习近平主席2016年新年贺词（双语版）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p759190/\">用错这些商