  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201510/93dc0c6e-eee8-443f-ac45-8d3a33ae3db3.jpg\" style=\"height: 418px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 14.4444px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center; width: 500px;\" /><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 14.4444px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 15.5556px; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span><strong><span>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Irreversible\" target=\"_blank\">Irreversible</a><br />\n\tIrreversible means the outcome cannot be returned to the original state. What is irreversible? Why is it so?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They observed the irreversible reaction... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) irreversible chemical reactions, such as explosion, cooking, burning, etc.<br />\n\t2) actions with irreversible consequences<br />\n\t3) the reverse drive on the car is broken<br />\n\t4) trying to balance an irreversible chemical equation<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;To the body, it would be like stepping on the gas and the brakes at the same time. The engine gets reved up, but is unable to move. The situation is obviously not sustainable as these two opposing actions are not meant to be carried out at the same time. The engine may be burnt out, causing irreversible damage. The same case applies to the body. The combination of these two drugs causes high stress to the body. As a result, the body is forced into a fight or flight response.&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166207526685/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p753092/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p753092\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761731/\">歪果仁也追太子妃升职记：五毛钱国剧你赢了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761789/\">最易记住的10个英文单词 不用背就知道！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761788/\">语言点精析：卡梅伦2016新年贺词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761771/\">囧研究：女人最爱自黑的五个点 你中枪了么</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761709/\">考据党观影报告：10个神探夏洛克大电影彩蛋</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761634/\">搞笑野生动物摄影奖：一个个都是影帝啊！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761738/\">2015负能量新闻TOP5：满屏逗比都忘吃药了吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p760669/\">心灵鸡汤：学学自信的人都是怎么做的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p761575/\">习近平主席2016年新年贺词（双语版）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p759190/\">用错这些商务词，会让你显得low（上）</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
